OL,4,CUber will continue to require riders to
OL,5,Cwear masks
OL,6, Uber has said passengers will still be
OL,7, required to wear a face covering when
OL,8, using its services after Covid
OL,9, restrictions are relaxed across Britain
OL,10, on Monday.
OL,12,FFace masks have been required in taxis
OL,13,Fand on public transport for the past
OL,14,Fyear to reduce the spread of the virus.
OL,16,FBut Uber has said it will keep its "no
OL,17,Fmask, no ride" policy in place.
OL,19,FThat's despite rules in England being
OL,20,Freplaced with guidance advising people
OL,21,Fto wear masks in enclosed spaces.
